para_trans: Government Circular No: Narrow-2024 / P.No.162 / Establishment
The scope of the study group shall be as follows: -
1. Simplification and streamlining of the process with a view to provide notified services to the citizens more easily.
Re-engineering the business process.
Creating a Common Application Form.
3. Develop procedures for linking services to Digi-Locker.
4. Fixation of time limit for preservation of records in respect of notified services.
5. Certain other services in the field office under the Department of Cultural Affairs State Service Rights.
To also recommend if they are to be notified under the Act.
Duration for submission to 3.अहव: -
The above study group should submit its report to the government within three months.
The study group may hold meetings as needed.
5. This Government Circular is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
